                    <span>This book is so well written, so cleanly designed and so perfectly illustrated that it is required reading to all nature lovers, particularly those interested in the strange, beautiful and other-wordly life of the deep sees. Brilliant and sure to appeal to ages ranging from 8 to 80 years old.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The blue planet</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
